"msg":"見到你咁講就好<br />\n我都一樣<br />\n原來係正常行為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"太長唔掹會勁痕，好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651dcb8a869b764e34dc6accf54e4ccb2b64d0f1","tid":2075261,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7j%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=805ef19c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7j%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=0fbd32c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a>"},{"pid":"09d7889e972239dba4ee74be9215cc9c66253cde","tid":2075261,"uid":12462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"直接胖手指掹啲又黑又粗嘅鼻毛 好有滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5292d3673b594bf1dc41614afbd50a7eab943c","tid":2075261,"uid":358318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:46:02.000Z","msg":"廿歲咁快就未老先衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇黎你都幾虧"},{"pid":"1f72fd0a03060b4cf07b23aa85a246e9c17d8b7d","tid":2075261,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f5292d3673b594bf1dc41614afbd50a7eab943c","tid":2075261,"uid":358318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T16:46:02.000Z","msg